text: Michele D. Presnell (born March 5, 1952) is a Republican member of the North Carolina General Assembly from Yancey County.http://votesmart.org/candidate/biography/134078/michele- presnell#.VWvfIGTBzGc She represents the 118th district in the North Carolina House. ==Honors== In 2018, Presnell was listed as a Champion of the Family in the NC Values Coalition Scorecard. ==References== Category:Living people Category:North Carolina Republicans Category:Women state legislators in North Carolina Category:21st-century American politicians Category:1952 births Category:21st-century American women politicians
title: Michele D. Presnell
